title: Guns n Roses Live in Paris 1992 XviD PreTV HiFi stereo
description: Never before released Pre-broadcast version of Guns'n'Roses Live in Paris 1992. this is an original transfer direct from a master 1992 VHS recording taken direct from the video/audio feed at the venue with no channel ident. Unfortunately this is not complete and starts part way through the song Attitude, the rest of the gig is there right to the end and beyond. Video is VHS and Audio is HiFi stereo with no broadcast compression. Duration 2h 19m
